Billy Joe Saunders and Chris Eubank Jnr could rematch in under six weeks after the pair reignited their war of words at a London press conference .
The pair clashed in their 12-round grudge match on November 29 with British , Commonwealth and European middleweight champions Saunders .
Now the duo are both set to fight at Wembley Arena on May 9 but not against each other .
Hall of Fame promoter Frank Warren challenged the pair fighting in May .